365
00:41:52.110 --> 00:41:53.611
I'm sort of an orphan.

366
00:41:53.779 --> 00:41:55.988
Oh. What about your friends?

367
00:41:56.156 --> 00:41:58.616
I have some, but I have to find them.

368
00:41:58.784 --> 00:42:01.410
I'll let them know
where I am tomorrow.

