535
01:08:03.055 --> 01:08:05.348
You know,
that Voight-Kampff test of yours...

536
01:08:06.391 --> 01:08:09.352
...did you ever take that test yourself?

537
01:08:21.073 --> 01:08:22.698
Deckard.

538
01:10:53.183 --> 01:10:54.892
I dreamt music.

539
01:11:00.065 --> 01:11:02.692
I didn't know if I could play.

540
01:11:04.361 --> 01:11:07.154
I remember lessons.

541
01:11:08.031 --> 01:11:11.951
I don't know if it's me
or Tyrell's niece.

542
01:11:16.540 --> 01:11:18.874
You play beautifully.

543
01:12:28.945 --> 01:12:31.447
Now you kiss me.

544
01:12:32.824 --> 01:12:34.283
I can't rely on my...

545
01:12:34.451 --> 01:12:37.119
Say, "Kiss me."

546
01:12:39.831 --> 01:12:41.749
Kiss me.

547
01:12:53.178 --> 01:12:59.725
