551
01:14:30.901 --> 01:14:34.195
- What you doing?
- I'm sorry. Just peeking.

552
01:14:34.362 --> 01:14:35.863
Oh.

553
01:14:38.116 --> 01:14:41.243
- How do I look?
- You look better.

554
01:14:41.411 --> 01:14:44.455
- Just better?
- Well...

555
01:14:44.623 --> 01:14:45.915
...you look beautiful.

556
01:14:49.503 --> 01:14:51.170
Thanks.

557
01:14:57.594 --> 01:14:59.512
How old are you?

558
01:15:01.431 --> 01:15:03.474
Twenty-five.

559
01:15:03.642 --> 01:15:06.602
- What's your problem?
- Methuselah syndrome.

560
01:15:06.770 --> 01:15:08.103
What's that?

561
01:15:08.271 --> 01:15:11.273
My glands, they grow old too fast.

562
01:15:12.442 --> 01:15:16.654
- Is that why you're still on Earth?
- Yeah. I couldn't pass the medical.

563
01:15:19.658 --> 01:15:20.866
Anyway...

564
01:15:21.034 --> 01:15:22.493
...I kind of like it here.

565
01:15:25.163 --> 01:15:27.122
I like you...

566
01:15:27.290 --> 01:15:28.541
...just the way you are.

567
01:15:31.795 --> 01:15:33.587
Hi, Roy.

568
01:15:33.755 --> 01:15:35.172
Hi.

569
01:15:35.340 --> 01:15:37.049
Gosh, you...

570
01:15:37.217 --> 01:15:39.510
