571
01:15:39.678 --> 01:15:42.054
This is the friend I
was telling you about.

572
01:15:42.222 --> 01:15:45.474
This is my savior, J.F. Sebastian.

573
01:15:45.642 --> 01:15:47.142
Sebastian.

574
01:15:47.811 --> 01:15:50.479
I like a man that stays put.

575
01:15:52.023 --> 01:15:55.359
You live here all by yourself, do you?

576
01:15:55.527 --> 01:15:56.569
Yes.

577
