590
01:17:36.044 --> 01:17:37.419
Because...

591
01:17:37.587 --> 01:17:39.755
...you're so different.

592
01:17:41.257 --> 01:17:43.342
You're so perfect.

593
01:17:45.845 --> 01:17:48.097
Yes.

594
01:17:48.264 --> 01:17:50.432
