601
01:18:12.872 --> 01:18:14.790
Like anything.

602
01:18:16.626 --> 01:18:21.463
We're no computers, Sebastian.
We're physical.

603
01:18:23.216 --> 01:18:25.467
I think, Sebastian...

604
01:18:25.635 --> 01:18:28.053
