605
01:18:28.221 --> 01:18:31.515
Very good, Pris. Now show him why.

606
01:18:58.418 --> 01:19:00.169
We've got a lot in common.

607
01:19:00.336 --> 01:19:02.588
- What do you mean?
- Similar problems.

608
01:19:02.756 --> 01:19:05.549
