641
01:22:16.324 --> 01:22:18.033
Queen...

642
01:22:19.702 --> 01:22:21.703
...bishop six.

643
01:22:22.705 --> 01:22:23.705
Hm.

644
01:22:26.834 --> 01:22:29.211
<i>Knight...</i>

645
01:22:29.379 --> 01:22:31.588
<i>...takes queen.</i>

646
01:22:38.388 --> 01:22:40.806
What's on your mind, Sebastian?

647
01:22:40.974 --> 01:22:42.432
What are you thinking about?

648
01:22:44.060 --> 01:22:46.269
ROY
Bishop to king seven.

649
01:22:46.437 --> 01:22:48.480
Checkmate.

650
01:22:48.648 --> 01:22:50.732
Bishop to king seven.
Checkmate, I think.

651
01:22:52.568 --> 01:22:55.779
Got a brainstorm, huh, Sebastian?

652
01:22:55.947 --> 01:22:58.907
Milk and cookies
kept you awake, huh?

653
01:22:59.075 --> 01:23:01.243
<i>Let's discuss this.</i>

654
01:23:01.411 --> 01:23:03.412
<i>You better come up, Sebastian.</i>

655
01:23:21.014 --> 01:23:22.973
Mr. Tyrell?

656
01:23:24.767 --> 01:23:26.435
I...

657
01:23:26.602 --> 01:23:28.520
I brought a friend.

658
01:23:34.777 --> 01:23:38.780
