684
01:25:13.626 --> 01:25:15.794
...the subject was dead
before he left the table.

685
01:25:16.003 --> 01:25:19.047
Then a repressor protein
that blocks the operating cells.

686
01:25:19.215 --> 01:25:23.218
Wouldn't obstruct replication, but it
does give rise to an error in replication.

687
01:25:23.386 --> 01:25:28.056
So that the newly formed DNA strand
carries a mutation...

688
01:25:28.224 --> 01:25:31.101
...and you've got a virus again.

689
01:25:31.269 --> 01:25:35.730
But this, all of this, is...

690
01:25:35.898 --> 01:25:37.482
...academic.

691
01:25:37.650 --> 01:25:40.152
You were made
as well as we could make you.

692
01:25:40.319 --> 01:25:42.070
But not to last.

693
01:25:42.905 --> 01:25:46.074
The light that burns twice as bright
burns half as long.

694
01:25:46.242 --> 01:25:50.453
And you have burned
so very, very brightly, Roy.

695
01:25:51.080 --> 01:25:52.831
Look at you.

696
01:25:53.040 --> 01:25:55.584
You're the prodigal son.

697
01:25:55.751 --> 01:25:59.254
You're quite a prize.

698
01:26:04.927 --> 01:26:06.428
I've done...

699
01:26:06.596 --> 01:26:08.263
...questionable things.

700
01:26:08.431 --> 01:26:10.307
Also extraordinary things.

701
01:26:10.933 --> 01:26:13.310
Revel in your time.

702
01:26:17.273 --> 01:26:21.776
Nothing the god of biomechanics
wouldn't let you in heaven for.

703
01:27:13.996 --> 01:27:16.748
Sorry, Sebastian.

704
01:27:17.124 --> 01:27:20.126
Come. Come.

705
01:28:06.549 --> 01:28:08.883
<i>Body identified with Tyrell...</i>

706
01:28:09.051 --> 01:28:11.386
<i>...is a 25-year-old male Caucasian.</i>

707
01:28:11.554 --> 01:28:14.389
<i>Name: Sebastian, J.F. Sebastian.</i>

708
01:28:14.557 --> 01:28:19.394
