735
01:37:13.345 --> 01:37:14.846
Come on, Deckard.

736
01:37:15.389 --> 01:37:18.599
I'm right here,
but you've gotta shoot straight.

737
01:37:19.935 --> 01:37:22.353
Straight doesn't seem
to be good enough!

738
01:37:22.521 --> 01:37:23.563
Now it's my turn.

739
01:37:25.482 --> 01:37:29.193
